'''Somtel''' ({{lang-en|''Somtel''}} {{lang-ar|''سومتيل''}}), waa shirkad isgaarsiin oo ku taala [[Somaliland]].Waxa ay ka mid tahay shirkadaha ka farcamay [[Dahabshiil]]<ref>[http://saraarmedia.com/blog/1398], " Somtel waxay ka mid tahay shirkadaha ka farcama Dahabshiil" </ref>. Shirkadaan waxa ay cagaheeda isku taagtey bishii [[Maarso]] 1998.

== Adeegyadda Somtel ==
Shirkadda somtel waa shirkad isticmaasho adeega xadhigla (wireless) ee casriga ah. Shirkadaan waa shirkadii ugu horeeysay ee [[Soomaaliya]] ka bilaawdo adeegyada [[3G]] iyo [[4G LTE]]. Shirkadani waxa xaruunteeda ugu ween ku taala wadada madaxtooyada [[Somaliland]] ee [[Hargeysa]], Sidoo kale waxaa shirkadan si rasmi ah uga hawl gashaa dhammaan wadanka oo dhan iyadoo xaruumo ku leh dhammaan gobolada dalka oo dhan.

==Magac==
Ereyga Somtel waxaa laga soo xigtay ereyada [[Ingiriiska|Afka Qalaad]] ku noqonaya "Somali Telecomunication"; taasi oo macnaheedu yahay "Isgaadhsiinta Soomaalida".

==Shirkado Shiraako la ah==
===O3b===
Bishii Nofember 2013, shirkada warisgaadhsiita O3b Networks, Ltd. waxay ku dhawaaqdey ineey Somtel wada galeen heshiis ah in O3b keeni doonto adeeg internet oo xawaarihiisu aad u sareeyo, isla markaana kharash badan ugu fadhiyin Somtel.<ref>[http://www.o3bnetworks.com/2816 O3b]</ref>

===Google===
Tan ilaa horaantii 2012, Somtel waxay heshiis la gashay shirkada [[Google]] si ay u isticmaasho adeega [[e-mail]]ka ee shirkadani.<ref>[https://support.google.com/chat/answer/1694772?hl=en]</ref> <ref>[http://somtelnetwork.net/services/mobilemessaging/]</ref>

==Moowjadaha==
Shirkada Somtel waxay ku shaqeeysa adeegyada kala ah [[GSM]] iyo [[4G LTE]], kuwaasi oo leh awood ka fiican kuwii hore. Intaas waxaa dheer adeegyo kale oo kala ah: [[3G]] 2100, [[2G]] 1800, 900 iyo LTE 800[[MHz]] 20 FDD.

